WEBVTT

02:04:48.108 --> 02:04:50.441
Why are you so adamant
that he should appear today itself?

02:04:50.441 --> 02:04:51.816
No, sir. I'm not adamant.

02:04:52.066 --> 02:04:53.899
But without instructions
from the police,

02:04:54.358 --> 02:04:55.441
what can I do, sir?

02:04:56.108 --> 02:04:58.108
You can get instructions
over the phone today.

02:04:58.149 --> 02:04:58.983
Yes.
